{"tid":2195571,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【無懼媽咪面】農夫山泉獲納入恒指綜合指數　9月22日起生效","createTime":"2020-09-09T09:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T09:17:44.000Z","uid":66271,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"56bc4a38517a24700aaf7b7b7a2d45ac15cf522a","tid":2195571,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:06:42.000Z","msg":"恒生指數公司宣布，由於農夫山泉股份(09633)符合恒生綜合指數的快速納入指數規則要求，相關指數的成份股將於9月21日收市後有下列變動，並於9月22日起生效。<br />\n<br />\n此舉意味該股有機會獲納入「北水」名單，惟此有待內地公布作實。<br />\n<br />\n農夫山泉周三(9日)收報33.2元，升0.3%，成交15億元。"},{"pid":"de3e359fbf9137489dd2a142d882a4f77b44ac89","tid":2195571,"uid":12463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:10:03.000Z","msg":"好在抽中2手仲未放"},{"pid":"0508304794698e0f079498dfd1d7d46598c04803","tid":2195571,"uid":295230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:11:42.000Z","msg":"上市幾日就入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n紅指果然係紅指"},{"pid":"54bdb6e62fca28ace051ad26c4703c94b6cd787c","tid":2195571,"uid":912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:12:25.000Z","msg":"憑咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f533ad5c8d743c7089abef9665ea8052aae6d0","tid":2195571,"uid":217778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:15:32.000Z","msg":"入左都可以跌，唔好睇小面神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9738df6b78536